lead_paragraph: China's Wu Minxia will make her bid to become the most decorated female Olympic diver at the Rio de Janeiro Games, fronting an attempt by her country to sweep all eight titles next month at the Maria Lenk Aquatics Centre.

headline.print_headline: Wu Eyes Diving Record as China Targets Sweep
